    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>The Power of Love&apos;s Ministry</strong>&mdash;Love&apos;s agencies have wonderful power, for they are divine. The soft answer that &ldquo;turneth away wrath,&rdquo; the love that &ldquo;suffereth long, and is kind,&rdquo; the charity that &ldquo;covereth a multitude of sins&rdquo;&mdash;would we learn the lesson, with what power for healing would our lives be gifted! How life would be transformed and the earth become a very likeness and foretaste of heaven!",
