    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "These precious lessons may be so simply taught as to be understood even by little children. The heart of the child is tender and easily impressed; and when we who are older become &ldquo;as little children,&rdquo; when we learn the simplicity and gentleness and tender love of the Saviour, we shall not find it difficult to touch the hearts of the little ones and teach them love&apos;s ministry of healing.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">1<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ed 114.1\" data-link=\"29.548\">Education, 114</span>.</span></a></sup>",
