    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Parents, give your children love: love in babyhood, love in childhood, love in youth. Do not give them frowns, but ever keep a sunshiny countenance.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">6<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 129, 1898\" data-link=\"14063.5866001\">Manuscript 129, 1898</span>.</span></a></sup>",
