    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Help your children to gain victories.... Surround them with an atmosphere of love. Thus you can subdue their stubborn dispositions.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">8<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 114, 1903\" data-link=\"14068.9441001\">Manuscript 114, 1903</span>.</span></a></sup>",
