    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Cultivate tenderness, affection, and love that have expression in little courtesies, in speech, in thoughtful attentions.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">13<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"YI 4-21-1886.7\" data-link=\"469.586\">The Youth&apos;s Instructor, April 21, 1886</span>.</span></a></sup>",
